text: Today, I took delivery of my stainless steel audio rack from Starlight Stainless Steel. I was shocked at how gorgeous and good looking the rack was, and it definitely exceeded my expectations. This rack is 100% custom-made - I provided the dimensions & the team from Starlight Stainless Steel created it to my dimensions. 100% would recommend anyone to custom made their stainless steel items from Starlight Stainless Steel

The Owner And their staff is very accommodating and always finds a solution to the problem.

They are well know for high quality work. I strongly recommend.

Solid products for starlight. Bought 2 fridges 2 steamers and hot water dispenser from them over the years. The first fridge I bought from them over 4 years ago still works very well. No issue at all.
Very responsive! Provided solution on what can be done.. Also suggestion to improve..   Definitely recommended!
Very responsive and prompt! Provided a lot of alternatives and suggestions on what can be done when I ran out of ideas as well. Definitely recommended! Thank you!
